.git
.gitignore
# Build artifacts — 9GB+; never in the build context.
target/
**/target/
rust/
*.log
# The Python oracle (post-2.0-flip): kept in-tree for golden-diffs but never part
# of any Rust image build context. The Rust portals own their assets under
# portals/*/assets and crates/bss-portal-ui/assets (decoupled from python-legacy).
# Not needed by any image build.
*.md
phases/
docs/
scenarios/
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
__pycache__
*.pyc
.mypy_cache
.ruff_cache
.pytest_cache
.hypothesis
.coverage
*.egg-info
.venv
.DS_Store
._.DS_Store
